Overview
Your challenge is to implement a functional and user-friendly web page using Next.js and TypeScript, based on a provided Figma design. You will connect this frontend to a mock API for data.
This task evaluates your ability to translate design into code, build reusable components, manage application state, and interact with a REST API, while following best practices in code structure and maintainability.
