Goal
The objective of this web assessment is to create a functional and user-friendly website that allows users to efficiently manage food items. The system should enable users to:
Search for food items quickly and accurately.
Add, edit, and remove food items with ease.
View a well-organized list of available food items.
The implementation should ensure a seamless user experience while maintaining data integrity and system responsiveness.
